INSTALL INTELLIJ IDEA
=====================
	download it from official web page
	un-tar file
	follow the instructions into INSTALL file


INSTALL GROOVY
=============
	curl -s get.sdkman.io | bash
	source "$HOME/.sdkman/bin/sdkman-init.sh"
	sdk install groovy


INSTALL GRADLE
==============
	sdk install gradle


IMPORT THE PROJECT TO INTELLIJ
==============================
	Just follow the tutorial in moodle to import gradle project
  -If there is any problem with jogl, jogamp or opengl libraries simply change anything in the build.gradle file and make sure that the libraries are imported.
	-If the problem still remains, try running it from the console by:
	  --go to View->ToolWindows->Terminal, then execute:
		--gradle compileGroovy
		-- ...and after that:
		--gradle run


SETUP GROOVY INTO INTELLIJ
==========================
	in terminal type:
	which gradle
		/home/cj/.sdkman/candidates/groovy/current
	follow the instructions in: https://www.bonusbits.com/wiki/HowTo:Add_Groovy_SDK_to_IntelliJ_IDEA


SETUP GRADLE INTO INTELLIJ
==========================
  in terminal type:
	which gradle
  	/home/cj/.sdkman/candidates/gradle/current
